---

---

<section class="team">
  <div class="team-photos">
    <div class="team-photos-track">
      <img src="/images/team-5.jpg" alt="Team" />
      <img src="/images/team-1.jpg" alt="Team" />
      <img src="/images/team-8.jpg" alt="Team" />
      <img src="/images/team-3.jpg" alt="Team" />
      <img src="/images/team-6.jpg" alt="Team" />
      <img src="/images/team-4.jpg" alt="Team" />
      <img src="/images/team-7.jpg" alt="Team" />
      <img src="/images/team-2.jpg" alt="Team" />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="team-content">
    <div class="team-text">
      <p class="team-description">
        Wir sind Sophie und Charlotte, die Gründerinnen von HyCoffee. Zwischen
        Ostafrika und Deutschland arbeiten wir mit Produzent:innen, Röstereien und
        der Wissenschaft zusammen, um klimaresiliente Anbausysteme zu fördern und
        außergewöhnliche Kaffees auf den Markt zu bringen. Unser Ziel: eine faire
        Kaffeebranche, die auch im Klimawandel bestehen kann.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="team-right">
      <h2 class="team-heading">Wer wir sind</h2>
      <a href="/ueber-uns" class="btn btn-secondary">
        <span>Secondary Button</span>
        <svg class="arrow" width="14" height="11" viewBox="0 0 14 11" fill="none">
          <path d="M1 5.5h12m0 0L8.5 1M13 5.5L8.5 10" stroke="white" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .team {
    background: var(--warm-grey-light);
    border: 1px solid var(--warm-dark-grey);
  }

  .team-photos {
    width: 100%;
    height: 181px;
    overflow: hidden;
    filter: grayscale(100%);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--warm-dark-grey);
  }

  .team-photos-track {
    display: flex;
    height: 100%;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .team-photos-track img {
    height: 100%;
    width: auto;
    object-fit: cover;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .team-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    padding: 80px 60px;
    gap: 60px;
    max-width: var(--container-max);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .team-text {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .team-description {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 36px;
    line-height: 36px;
    color: var(--warm-dark-grey);
  }

  .team-right {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .team-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 75px;
    line-height: 70.3px;
    letter-spacing: -1.5px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--warm-dark-grey);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    background: var(--warm-dark-grey);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 10px 24px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 20px;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .arrow {
    width: 14px;
    height: 11px;
  }
</style>
